data.description: Immaculately presented and meticulously cared for, this beautiful home offers a superb split-bedroom floor plan with separated laundry, dining nook and den - currently utilized as a spacious home office. Immediately upon entering the property, your eye is drawn down the stunning entryway which spans the entire length of the home. Enjoy stainless steel appliances, granite, tray ceilings, diagonal tile and strategic window placement allowing for an abundance of light to infiltrate the entire home. Backing onto the preserve, you can relax in peace, quiet and privacy from your screened and paved lanai. The garage is oversized allowing for optimal storage and parking. Low HOA fees include resort-style heated pool/spa, gym, clubhouse, basketball, tennis and so much more. External pest control, lawn maintenance, irrigation water, cable and high-speed internet are also covered.
